告诉大家，1.15在性能上做了很多改善，并且发现了我的以前一些设置项(Flag)的问题
几周前，我开始调整这些设置项来解决这个问题，并进一步优化它们，并且做了大量的测试
一个多星期以来，我们在最新的一组设置项上保持服务器允许稳定，并且每个使用者都感到了巨大的改进
现在，为了改进Minecraft最新版本Java的GC，需要使用这些设置项
请参见https://mcflags.emc.gs
是的，这些设置项仍然适用于旧版本的MC,甚至在旧版本效果更好。旧版本中的缺陷不会受到太大的影响，而且新版本设置也无需担心！这些新参数可以降低GC回收的间隔时间
许多服务器已经开始切换新的启动参数，一些MC服务商(Hosts)甚至正在帮助服主设置它们
一些MC服务商甚至告诉我它可以节省CPU使用：）
另外，从所有的GC研究中发现，很多人都在更新版本的Java来评估ZGC。我的建议是避免使用ZGC,除非你满足两个条件:
1）版本为Java 14+，
2）至少有15-20GB的最大内存(分配给Xmx)
如果你在内存上低于这个值，就像大多数服务器一样，ZGC最终会破坏你的性能!
即使有人吹捧它可以减少延迟,那都是骗人的鬼话
如果您想知道更多，可以到Discord论坛询问或查找关键词“ZGC Allocation Stall”
原话:
FYI everyone, 1.15 did a number on performance, and uncovered an issue with my old flag set.

A few weeks ago I started tweaking the flags to fix that issue and optimize them even more, and did a lot of beta testing.

We've been stable on the latest set of flags for over a week now, and has shown massive improvement for everyone using them.

These flags are now pretty much required to improve the GC of Java for Minecraft's latest versions.

see https://mcflags.emc.gs

And yes, these flags still work on older versions of MC! And will do even better there. The flaw in the old set did not get hit at all much on the older versions, but the new set will remove all worry, as well as lower GC pause times.

Lots of servers have started switching, as well as some MC Hosts are even helping set them up now.
Some MC Hosts have even told me it is saving them on CPU usage too

Also, from all the GC research again, a lot of people have been evaluating ZGC in newer Java. My recommendation is to avoid ZGC unless you are both: 1) On Java 14, and 2) Have at least 15-20GB of memory given to Xmx.

If you are lower than that on memory, like most servers are, ZGC will end up destroying your performance, even when it says it has low pauses, the pause information is deceptive. If you're curious to know more, ask on Discord or look up "ZGC Allocation Stall"

该参数:The JVM 启动参数 – MC 1.15 更新准确使用这些设置, 只更改 Xmx 和 Xms. 这些设置可以根据任何大小的内存（甚至只有500MB）下运行且自行调整java -Xms10G -Xmx10G -XX:+UseG1GC -XX:+ParallelRefProcEnabled -XX:MaxGCPauseMillis=200 -XX:+UnlockExperimentalVMOptions -XX:+DisableExplicitGC -XX:-OmitStackTraceInFastThrow -XX:+AlwaysPreTouch  -XX:G1NewSizePercent=30 -XX:G1MaxNewSizePercent=40 -XX:G1HeapRegionSize=8M -XX:G1ReservePercent=20 -XX:G1HeapWastePercent=5 -XX:G1MixedGCCountTarget=8 -XX:InitiatingHeapOccupancyPercent=15 -XX:G1MixedGCLiveThresholdPercent=90 -XX:G1RSetUpdatingPauseTimePercent=5 -XX:SurvivorRatio=32 -XX:MaxTenuringThreshold=1 -Dusing.aikars.flags=true -Daikars.new.flags=true -jar 核心文件名.jar nogui
上次更新: Apr 06 2020 3:30PM EST
注意: 这些设置还在测试阶段。如果遇到旧一代的GC问题，请到Paper的Discord界面反馈
